        <imgdir name="0">
            <int name="ask" value="1" />
            <string name="0" value="What is it?!!\r\n#b#L0#I have come to see you and your new method.#l" />
            <string name="1" value="So what do you want to talk about?!! If you have something to say, make it quick!\r\n#b#L0#Oh..okay! I'd like to learn the new method you discovered...(He's intimidating.)#l" />
            <string name="2" value="Good! I like your attitude! After working on this for years, I was finally able to discover a new method that will enable me to forego blacksmithing and produce an item purely out of alchemy. Unlike the blacksmithing technique, which requires years of practice, this method can be easily mastered by studying the theory behind it! After discovering this groundbreaking new method, I was looking for an apprentice that is willing to spread the word on this! What do you think? Are you ready to learn this?!\r\n#L0##bYes, I am!#l" />
            <string name="3" value="Great! My new method is called #e#b#q1007##k#n! Are you ready to start?" />
